description: The libraries contained in this experiment come from the whole cell fraction of independent isolates of mobilized CD14+ monocytes. They are stranded PE101 Illumina Hi-Seq RNA-Seq libraries from rRNA-depleted Poly-A+ RNA > 200 nucleotides in size.
